CLOUD SERVER :-
Cloud Server" ke baare mein bataya hai. Cloud server ek remote server hota hai jo internet ke through access 
kiya ja sakta hai aur data storage aur processing ke liye use kiya ja sakta hai. Iske through hum real-time data collection aur analysis kar sakte hain.

Is project mein cloud server ka use isliye kiya jata hai ki jab car accident hota hai toh sensors ki readings cloud server mein collect ki jati hai
aur phir us data ko process karke emergency services ko notify kiya jata hai.
Cloud server par aap ek application program interface (API) develop kar sakte hain jo device se data collect karega aur use analysis
karke notifications bhejega.

Aap Amazon Web Services (AWS), Microsoft Azure, Google Cloud Platform jaise cloud service providers ka use kar sakte hain jo 
aapko ek scalable aur reliable infrastructure provide karenge jiske through aap apne application ko deploy kar sakte hain.




